PortSystem 1.0
name		libsndfile
version		1.0.1
categories	audio
maintainers	sean@sfarc.net
description	Library for reading and writing audio files
long_description	libsndfile is a C library for reading and writing sound files such as AIFF, AU and WAV files through one standard interface.  It can currently read/write 8, 16, 24 and 32-bit PCM files as well as 32-bit floating point WAV files and a number of compressed formats.
platforms	darwin
master_sites	http://www.zipworld.com.au/~erikd/libsndfile/
checksums	md5 bb328567ad639b72d22f7bf3b31550c7

